name: Anday Kay Kabab Recipe | Shireen Anwar | Masala TV
ingredients: Ingredients for Anday Kay Kabab Recipe: Potatoes (boiled & mashed) 250 grams Eggs (boiled & chopped) 4 Onion (chopped) half cup Spring Onions (chopped) half cup Coriander leaves (chopped) 2 tbsp Red Pepper (crushed) 1 Â½ tsp Green Chilies (chopped) 4 Allspice half tsp Salt 1 tsp Bread Slices (mashed) 4 Egg 1 + 1 Bread Crumbs for coating Oil for frying
instructions: Mix all the ingredients very well with 1 egg, make into small kababs. Dip in the second beaten egg. Coat in bread crumbs deep fry in fry pan.
